results.title: A Preliminary Investigation on the Effects of Atenolol for Treating Symptoms of Anxiety.
results.text_hl: More detailed examinations are needed to further determine whether @<m>CHEMICAL_Atenolol</m> @CHEMICAL_MESH:D001262 @@@atenolol@@@ is a viable alternative or augmenting agent to @CHEMICAL_Propranolol @CHEMICAL_MESH:D011433 @@@propranolol@@@, @CHEMICAL_Benzodiazepines @CHEMICAL_MESH:D001569 @@@benzodiazepines@@@, and antidepressants for @DISEASE_Anxiety_Disorders @DISEASE_MESH:D001008 @@@anxiety disorders@@@ and @<m>DISEASE_Trauma_and_Stressor_Related_Disorders</m> @DISEASE_MESH:D000068099 @@@trauma-related disorders@@@.
